"""
app.py — MixABTest GPU edition.  Dear PyGui front-end.

Architecture:
  - DPG render loop runs at display refresh rate (vsync=True).
  - Audio engine (player.py) runs its own sounddevice thread — unchanged.
  - A single _update_tick() is registered with dpg.set_frame_callback to
    poll the audio engine position and push updated visuals every frame.
  - Waveform, meter, and spectrum rendering is done via the renderers/
    sub-package (all numpy + DPG set_value calls).
  - OS-level file drag-and-drop is handled by win_drop.py (Win32 IDropTarget).
"""

